Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.37,0:00:13.90,OP English,,0,0,0,,Just work it! ♥ And do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.90,0:00:15.56,OP English,,0,0,0,,Don't forget to catch and release yo!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.57,0:00:21.04,OP English,,0,0,0,,{\fscx90}I sweat! (Fuu!) I sweat! (Fuu!) And throw in a Darlin' darlin' FREEZE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.40,0:00:26.57,OP English,,0,0,0,,Feeling crummy! Something's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.57,0:00:28.46,OP English,,0,0,0,,I love you so! Oops! I screwed one upsie-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.46,0:00:29.80,OP English,,0,0,0,,A nail biter! A steel beater!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.80,0:00:31.46,OP English,,0,0,0,,Gourmet eater! Cut that out, already!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.46,0:00:33.38,OP English,,0,0,0,,Is that new blushing flower...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:34.98,OP English,,0,0,0,,...considered a normal girl, or what?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.98,0:00:38.14,OP English,,0,0,0,,Wowzers! Only for me? Pork chops! Firm noodles! Fill 'er up again!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.73,0:00:46.37,OP English,,0,0,0,,BON-BON Cheerleaders!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.37,0:00:47.97,OP English,,0,0,0,,Let's get! Cherry pie!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.97,0:00:49.58,OP English,,0,0,0,,RAN-RAN Welcome party!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.58,0:00:51.15,OP English,,0,0,0,,Look up! Sensation!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.15,0:00:54.20,OP English,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leavin' an impression... Asteroids.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:55.76,OP English,,0,0,0,,Crashed! And burned! Shockers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.76,0:00:57.60,OP English,,0,0,0,,Break into song! Crunch time!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.60,0:00:58.78,OP English,,0,0,0,,Take it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:03.19,OP English,,0,0,0,,I'll still be laughing in the end!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.19,0:01:10.05,OP English,,0,0,0,,'Cause it's a sailor uniform. ←Q.E.D.!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.05,0:01:12.36,OP English,,0,0,0,,It's only Monday!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.36,0:01:15.94,OP English,,0,0,0,,And I'm already blue. What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.94,0:01:22.68,OP English,,0,0,0,,I'd rather wear my summer clothes. ←So cute!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.89,0:01:25.98,OP English,,0,0,0,,3 pics incoming! That's a toughie to pick! Ooh {\fe128\fscx85\fscy85}☆ {The star doesn't render in the kara font!}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.98,0:01:29.98,OP English,,0,0,0,,Just work it! (Yeah!) To the limit! (Yeah!) My Darlin' darlin' PLEASE!!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.76,0:01:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We switch to summer uniforms today.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.27,0:01:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone like Konata will probably show up in her winter uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.64,0:01:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,At least one person in our class will forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Onee-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.03,0:01:50.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one in this house.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Rats!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.98,0:01:58.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgot to sign up for the TV drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.53,0:01:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Bah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.22,0:02:00.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I kinda wanted the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.77,0:02:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,An apron from Apron of Love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.10,0:02:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Not enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.75,0:02:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You forgot because you don't have enough love.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.68,0:02:08.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.44,0:02:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,More like I've been busy with student council stuff and tests.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope, nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.20,0:02:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are just excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.07,0:02:20.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't put me on the same level as someone who only ever thinks about having fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.04,0:02:22.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And the way you put it really pisses me off!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.80,0:02:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you win a drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.46,0:02:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,To put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.54,0:02:28.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.20,0:02:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.14,0:02:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a loveless woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.40,0:02:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.03,0:02:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you jot down the usual stuff you're not going to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.73,0:02:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you put on yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.71,0:02:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff that'll help me win.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.51,0:02:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Good handwriting is a fundamental must.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.26,0:02:47.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to design a postcard that just begs to be drawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.59,0:02:48.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.66,0:02:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.17,0:02:54.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Use a fluorescent marker to draw a border around the postcard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:56.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.21,0:03:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you add a picture related to the prize.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.27,0:03:01.84,Default,,0,0,0,,A picture, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.83,0:03:04.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't draw very well, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.81,0:03:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,...just send in as many entries as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.68,0:03:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I can probably handle that.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.97,0:03:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.01,0:03:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter how many you send, write each one out without using a printer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And send out a hundred each time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.73,0:03:22.79,Default,,0,0,0,,A hundred!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.79,0:03:24.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.86,0:03:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that cost a lot?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.58,0:03:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fighting for something you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.96,0:03:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That calls for passion and guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.39,0:03:34.40,Default,,0,0,0,,But wouldn't it be cheaper just to buy it, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Some things in this world can't be bought with money.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you fit a hundred postcards in a mailbox?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.44,0:03:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't send them all at once...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.92,0:03:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...but a few here and a few there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.77,0:03:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,And over the course of a few days.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.55,0:03:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Depending on who's running the drawing...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...you might get caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.01,0:03:57.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, sometimes you're better off without the tricky stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.18,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes it's the exact opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.88,0:04:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,So, what do we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.43,0:04:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Like I said...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.35,0:04:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Love!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.95,0:04:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.89,0:04:04.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, if you want to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.82,0:04:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...glance through free newspapers and flyers...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.03,0:04:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...and look for drawings that probably aren't going to attract many people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll have a high chance of winning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.13,0:04:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll give it a try!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.84,0:04:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the love in that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.87,0:04:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, for twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.48,0:04:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...you don't look anything like each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.13,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That's 'cause we're two-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:31.12,Default,,0,0,0,,So, it's more like comparing sisters.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.70,0:04:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,One-egg twins look exactly the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,...but two-egg twins can be...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,...pretty different in appearance and personality.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.37,0:04:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.72,0:04:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa is laid-back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.85,0:04:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...but Kagami is pretty psycho.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.03,0:04:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.30,0:04:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had the same hairstyles with the same ribbons...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.86,0:04:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...you might end up looking the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.69,0:04:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,No good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.41,0:04:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami could never be the cutesy type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.86,0:04:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Zip it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.68,0:04:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't insult me with your weird fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.53,0:04:57.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Can you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.98,0:04:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.68,0:04:59.68,Default,,0,0,0,,With twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.68,0:05:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Even when they're raised separately...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,...they end up having similar lifestyles and significant others.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.42,0:05:08.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And sometimes they end up marrying another pair of twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.81,0:05:11.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And when one of them is in danger...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.14,0:05:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...the other one can sense it from a completely different place.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.99,0:05:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,There are all kinds of mysterious phenomena.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.25,0:05:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,So, can't you use telepathy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.35,0:05:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Give it a spin.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.67,0:05:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Abracadabra!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:23.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You read way too much manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.30,0:05:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Same with ManaKana...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.80,0:05:26.09,Default,,0,0,0,,ManaKana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.09,0:05:29.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that they have a few differences.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, Mana is the careful one...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...and Kana is the optimistic one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And apparently they sound a little different when they sing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.15,0:05:37.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.85,0:05:42.31,Default,,0,0,0,,ManaKana thought they were two-egg twins for a long time...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.31,0:05:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,...but they recently learned that they were actually one-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.47,0:05:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.22,0:05:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it really that surprising?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.86,0:05:51.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The definitions for one-egg and two-egg twins...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...have changed recently.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.07,0:05:57.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means that you could be one-egg twins.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.21,0:05:59.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Your identical traits would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.48,0:06:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You both likes sweets, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.07,0:06:03.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Love 'em.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.85,0:06:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're both left-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.18,0:06:08.09,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.10,0:06:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your favorite color?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.34,0:06:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,White maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.34,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Black.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.18,0:06:13.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The same colors as your souls.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.06,0:06:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What was that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:22.05,Default,,0,0,0,,All this talk about eggs and black and white cookies has made me hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.05,0:06:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody was talking about food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.29,0:06:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It's suffocating in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.43,0:06:34.88,Default,,0,0,0,,We just got on and I'm already sweating.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.88,0:06:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's that time of year.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.12,0:06:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.84,0:06:41.83,Default,,0,0,0,,They haven't turned on the air conditioning yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.85,0:06:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:48.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Hot...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.71,0:06:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ladybug Samba, punk version.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.81,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my cousins is getting married this month.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.16,0:07:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So, she'll be a June bride.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.68,0:07:03.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds wonderful.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How does this...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.15,0:07:10.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...wet and gloomy season supposedly signify happiness?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.11,0:07:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why does getting married in June make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.17,0:07:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,The name June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...is generally said to be...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.23,0:07:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...derived from the name of the Roman goddess, Juno.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:24.79,Default,,0,0,0,,In Greek mythology...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.79,0:07:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,...Juno is known as Hera...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.19,0:07:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,...the goddess of marriage and fertility.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.89,0:07:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is why those who get married in Hera's month, the month of June...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:37.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...are said to receive her protection and blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.33,0:07:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,But wasn't Hera Zeus's wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.77,0:07:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I have this image of Hera being extremely jealous...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.83,0:07:48.07,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I'm not feeling this happy thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.07,0:07:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.92,0:07:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you rather wear a dress or a kimono for your wedding?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.34,0:07:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I would wear a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.46,0:07:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been my dream since I was a child.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd also go with a dress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.25,0:08:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,But a kimono would also be nice...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.14,0:08:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna wear both!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.40,0:08:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,They have miniskirts and really colorful dresses these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.85,0:08:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A miniskirt wedding dress?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.65,0:08:16.05,Default,,0,0,0,,It'd look really cute with lots of frills on the hem.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.05,0:08:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.52,0:08:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Lots of frills!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.80,0:08:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.97,0:08:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Angel Salvia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.99,0:08:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.59,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair makes you look like Daisy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,So a yellow top and miniskirt it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.99,0:08:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.97,0:08:32.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd probably look good in a miniskirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.54,0:08:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.57,0:08:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dress is important...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.76,0:08:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the person you're getting married to is also important.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.63,0:08:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,A childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Or a rich lady?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough choice to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.88,0:08:44.91,Default,,0,0,0,,One has lots of money...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.91,0:08:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,...and the ability to cast Beho*mi and I***zun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.70,0:08:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But as far as feelings are concerned...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.08,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Bianca, hands down!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.75,0:08:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.97,0:08:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the true love type, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.57,0:08:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought you'd go for the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,No comeback, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.11,0:09:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yo, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.54,0:09:06.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got a question about a game I borrowed the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.57,0:09:07.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.08,0:09:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hold it right there, Kagaminya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it more fun when you figure it out yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.28,0:09:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,You have a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.49,0:09:15.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.29,0:09:18.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you understand that you should do things yourself...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.60,0:09:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'll do your own homework from now on, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:25.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't the detectives in manga and TV shows...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.41,0:09:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...run into an awful lot of murders?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.37,0:09:30.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Like in Conan or Kindaichi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.57,0:09:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There wouldn't be a story otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.44,0:09:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.36,0:09:36.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't they just solve normal cases?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.46,0:09:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Normal?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Like, travel around Japan in search of missing persons.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.47,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Tailing people would translate well into a game.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:46.55,Default,,0,0,0,,With plenty of thrill and suspense.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:47.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.64,0:09:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You could also conduct investigations into unfaithful wives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.09,0:09:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Or look for pets that ran away?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep, yep!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But would that be fun to watch?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.55,0:09:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably no fun at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.61,0:10:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Also...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.40,0:10:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Cases in real life...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.94,0:10:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,...don't really use any brilliant tricks...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.79,0:10:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,...like the ones you find in manga and TV shows.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.63,0:10:10.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess not.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.04,0:10:14.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Fabricated fingerprints that can't be detected through a luminol reaction.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.43,0:10:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Stuff that's a step ahead of forensic labs.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.02,0:10:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.70,0:10:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Anything too good might lead to copycats.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.07,0:10:22.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Or be too sensitive for broadcast.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.37,0:10:23.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, or that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.63,0:10:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,The really hard cases end without anyone realizing they happened or go unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be wrong in so many ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.17,0:10:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you hate how it's been constantly raining the past few days?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.87,Default,,0,0,0,,You're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.50,0:10:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,And I used to like rain...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.41,0:10:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You get soaked...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.01,0:10:45.81,Default,,0,0,0,,...and you can't hang clothes out to dry...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.81,0:10:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I've never really liked it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.03,0:10:49.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you like rain, Kona-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.21,0:10:55.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Because baseball games would be canceled and I'd get to watch anime.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.12,0:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds just like something you would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They have a lot more dome stadiums now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.63,0:11:06.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.14,0:11:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You often see idiots and geniuses going into the same school in anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.10,0:11:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Cease that immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Bite me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.87,0:11:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Get lost, neener-neener!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.73,0:11:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that actually kinda strange?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,If you put it that way...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.76,0:11:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...in some recent anime...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.94,0:11:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...the teacher looks the same age as the students.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.04,0:11:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Or even younger.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.47,0:11:29.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Sensei.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.77,0:11:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, Ta*****na-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.18,0:11:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The world's always been interested in watching...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.08,0:11:38.50,Default,,0,0,0,,...the gap between physical age and mental age.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.50,0:11:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.19,0:11:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,You shouldn't question it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.09,0:11:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,In fact, wouldn't a student who's really different from everyone else...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.06,0:11:47.01,Default,,0,0,0,,...be the real mystery?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.81,0:11:49.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.59,0:11:52.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I agree one hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be saying this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I don't know how you got into this school, Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good at putting stuff off till the night before...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.62,0:12:00.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...so you didn't study until the night before, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:06.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.20,0:12:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean she really did?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.67,0:12:08.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.31,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I couldn't have pulled it off in one night.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.01,0:12:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That gave me a scare.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.20,0:12:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,But I'm impressed that you actually kept studying.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.04,0:12:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Did a quiz game come out for DS or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.75,0:12:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,My dad set some conditions.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.68,0:12:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,A D-rank would mean a Pippin.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.11,0:12:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A C-rank would mean a 3DO.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.70,0:12:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,A B-rank would mean a PS2.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.70,0:12:26.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Papa Izumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.81,0:12:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really know how to deal with your daughter, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.26,0:12:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I've been wondering...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.00,0:12:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't the real mystery how Tsukasa's in the same school as us?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:41.56,Default,,0,0,0,,She said it without even blinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.05,0:12:45.88,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Come back in ten years!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.69,0:12:44.91,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Woo-hoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.88,Default-Right,,0,0,0,,Curses!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.91,0:12:45.88,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,I won again!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.88,0:12:47.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't beat her at fighting games.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.61,0:12:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,She's spent way more time than I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.98,0:12:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Challenge me to a different game if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.07,0:12:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.48,0:12:56.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then next is...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.08,0:12:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,A quiz game!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:12:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.50,0:13:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost to Konata in a game of knowledge?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.32,0:13:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.22,0:13:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.62,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Humiliated.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.13,0:13:07.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...she memorized the question order?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.62,0:13:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Her memory is incredible when it comes to gaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.92,0:13:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What should we play next?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.27,0:13:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't be in such a hurry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.32,0:13:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? That's weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.17,0:13:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you have a really easy party game?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.36,0:13:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know all the games I have?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.61,0:13:26.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You could probably beat me at that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.27,0:13:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It just stunk!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.59,0:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You've barely eaten any snacks, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.59,0:13:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, you wolf them down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.56,0:13:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no real reason for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.41,0:13:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.52,0:13:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dieting for summer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.73,0:13:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Not like you have anyone to show your swimsuit off to.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's none of your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.00,0:13:45.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.78,0:13:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you guys born on Tanabata?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.78,0:13:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't your birthday soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,What about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You remembered our birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.16,0:13:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Seventeen's right before the big one.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.33,0:13:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,What does that mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:00.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In the year before a critical year...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:04.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...unlucky things begin to happen.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.31,0:14:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,As our birthday approaches...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.70,0:14:08.78,Default,,0,0,0,,...I'm getting worried...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.78,0:14:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,...so I bought a bunch of wards...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.98,0:14:13.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...and power stones.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.42,0:14:15.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That sounds like fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.11,0:14:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure is!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.28,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't stop buying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.93,0:14:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We have wards against rage at our place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.64,0:14:21.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Er, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.32,0:14:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Wards against evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.58,0:14:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Wards against rage, hah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Like...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:29.53,Default,,0,0,0,,We ensure safe pregnancy and protect you from traffic accidents at the same time!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.59,0:14:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.12,0:14:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know that your birthday is Ponytail Day?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.17,0:14:37.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.31,0:14:39.73,Default,,0,0,0,,But why July 7th?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:43.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Because Vega from the Tanabata legend had a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.64,0:14:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like a stretch.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.52,0:14:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,There's a Japan Ponytail Society...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...and they give an award every year to a celebrity who they think would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:14:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,But I have a feeling that anyone would look good with a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.21,0:15:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure about that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.74,0:15:09.77,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair's the shortest...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.77,0:15:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,...so it's barely a ponytail.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.83,0:15:13.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But a little ponytail's pretty cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.93,0:15:15.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Yours also looks good, Kona-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.93,0:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You could go with that on an everyday basis.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.52,0:15:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:21.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.15,0:15:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Onee-chan also...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.70,0:15:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami's is...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.78,0:15:30.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.81,0:15:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I get the idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.63,0:15:33.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll undo it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,All manly like a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drunks often wear ties around their head?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.44,0:15:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that supposed to mean something?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.40,0:15:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.59,0:15:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't that just when the guy loosens the tie...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...and tries to pull it off over his head...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.16,0:15:51.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...but it gets stuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.09,0:15:56.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...it's a lot weirder that they're always carrying a takeout box.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:15:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Takeout box?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The thing Kato-chan from the Drifters carries.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.96,0:16:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not getting it...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.55,0:16:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Drunks these days...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.10,0:16:09.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...pretty much always have a tie around their head and a takeout box in their hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.39,0:16:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.31,0:16:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope Vega and Altair meet this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.27,0:16:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Shine. Shine. Shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.29,0:16:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hope those rage wards of yours can deliver a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.11,0:16:20.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Mind your own business.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,They're giving away all varieties of QUO cards at Comp Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.90,0:16:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.87,0:16:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always collecting QUO cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.06,0:16:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,...but do you ever use them?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.11,0:16:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.65,0:16:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Then why spend the effort?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.21,0:16:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it natural to want any item...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.70,0:16:37.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...related to a series you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.61,0:16:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,As a fan. As a collector.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.55,0:16:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.66,0:16:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...if you're never gonna use them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.97,0:16:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't use them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.54,0:16:45.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to take good care of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.13,0:16:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It really pisses me off when I see someone use one.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You're not supposed to use these things!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.77,0:16:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Much less auction them off or sell them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.31,0:16:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Using them makes you a surefire failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.74,0:17:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...as a fan and as a collector!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.04,0:17:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I really can't say anything when you're so worked up.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.92,0:17:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In my case, I need at least three.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.68,0:17:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,One for preservation.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.68,0:17:10.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I keep it in a special case.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Then one to take out occasionally and look at.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.12,0:17:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the last one for?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.42,0:17:14.89,Default,,0,0,0,,An extra.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.89,0:17:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.74,0:17:22.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you always want two or three of something you like?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.41,0:17:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.26,0:17:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just a geek.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.89,0:17:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.74,0:17:28.34,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.34,0:17:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I kind of understand what you're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.40,0:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd expect Tsukasa to be popular with guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.60,Default,,0,0,0,,...but I've never heard anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.60,0:17:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsukasa's a little plain and doesn't really stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.35,0:17:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't it because she's got a scary sister guarding her like a hawk?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.93,0:17:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you say something?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.66,0:17:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not sure if I'm really plain...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.58,0:17:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,...or it's more that Kona-chan and Yuki-chan are really unique.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san knows all kinds of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,And she's pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.30,0:17:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Has a good figure.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.44,0:17:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Wears glasses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.61,0:17:57.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hates the dentist.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:17:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Clumsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.29,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Hey now.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.58,0:17:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally clueless.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.29,0:18:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You kinda derailed there?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:04.51,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's true that I haven't heard anything about Miyuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.51,0:18:06.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe it's because she's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.04,0:18:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...that everyone's afraid to approach her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I doubt that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.81,0:18:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,She's kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.78,0:18:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,...and really good at helping others.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.15,0:18:12.40,Default,,0,0,0,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.40,0:18:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe a lot of guys ask her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.65,0:18:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,But she turns them down?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Turns them down, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.76,0:18:18.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.33,0:18:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe she doesn't realize that they're asking her out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.04,0:18:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.55,0:18:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Yuki-chan can be a little clueless...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.57,0:18:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...so an indirect approach might not work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.91,0:18:30.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, the guys in your class are hopeless.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.64,0:18:32.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't a single one of them have the guts...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.89,0:18:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,...to confess his passionate feelings to Miyuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:36.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess not...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.97,0:18:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have enough maniacs in our class.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.49,0:18:43.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san's type is usually a bigger hit with maniacs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.34,0:18:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Maniacs, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.87,0:18:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.39,0:18:51.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's already this late.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.59,0:18:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll need to excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.53,0:18:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.61,0:18:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please, continue to enjoy yourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll excuse myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.96,0:19:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.65,0:19:04.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Buh-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.80,0:19:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.98,0:19:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Going on with the story...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.77,0:19:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,...that person was actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.52,0:19:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm terribly sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.37,0:19:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.76,0:19:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.54,0:19:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, oh, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that always happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.74,0:19:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it the other day.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.94,0:19:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.38,0:19:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody does it at least once.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.84,0:19:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Konata?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.07,0:19:29.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.46,0:19:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what you call moe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,That was what you call an element of turning people on.}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.77,0:19:33.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.80,0:19:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.68,0:19:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Good lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.89,0:19:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's another whoo-whoo happy episode of Lucky Channel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.61,0:19:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm your navigator, Kogami Akira.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.67,0:19:49.07,Default,,0,0,0,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.07,0:19:49.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Akira-sama's assistant, Shiraishi Minoru.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.66,0:19:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a pleasure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.49,0:19:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,The two of us have now done this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.77,0:19:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ta-da!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Three times after today!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you feel about it, Shiraishi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.27,0:20:02.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you gotten used to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.25,0:20:03.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.15,0:20:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not yet...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.35,0:20:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,So sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.10,0:20:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like Shiraishi-san hasn't opened up to me yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.23,0:20:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And it looks like we're sitting further apart than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:16.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this what they mean by emotional distance?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.26,0:20:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Sob.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-That's not true!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.40,0:20:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Shuffle.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.97,0:20:20.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.79,0:20:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get rollin'!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.49,0:20:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.10,0:20:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got something the fans will love today!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.03,0:20:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.09,0:20:31.19,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be doing our first introduction for a member of the regular cast!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.19,0:20:32.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Da! Da-da-dum!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:33.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.53,0:20:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll be introducing Takara Miyuki-san today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.78,0:20:37.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.18,0:20:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,The class representative, well-mannered, kn-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.46,0:20:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowledgeable.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.51,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Knowledgeable...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...in both literary and culinary arts. A perfect person.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.13,0:20:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Shiraishi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.79,0:20:49.24,Default,,0,0,0,,You know Miyuki-san, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.24,0:20:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,But of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.84,0:20:52.71,Default,,0,0,0,,She's so wonderful, yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.71,0:20:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,First, there's her glasses!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,And then she's pretty as a button.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.05,0:20:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,With those looks...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.42,0:21:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'd expect her to be hard to approach...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.21,0:21:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...but she's actually a friendly person...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.97,0:21:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I wish you'd talk that much on the radio show...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.24,0:21:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop talking when it's about Miyuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.61,0:21:10.95,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.26,0:21:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.20,0:21:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Takara Miyuki-san, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.23,0:21:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,A pretty face.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.45,0:21:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,With large breasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,And various other turn-ons.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.52,0:21:21.95,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Akira-sama, that's a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.63,0:21:21.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't she so lucky to be a pretty character?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,The maniacs loves her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:25.45,Default-Alt,,0,0,0,,Uh, maniacs is a little...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.89,0:21:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,But you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.55,0:21:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,If it's maniacs you want, I'm a huge hit with those lolicons...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:29.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Too bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.39,0:21:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.00,0:21:32.16,Default,,0,0,0,,And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.16,0:21:39.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Send us any questions or comments about the show please!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.14,0:21:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look forward to next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.86,0:21:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,So what's she really like?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.55,0:21:47.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.15,0:21:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.06,0:21:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't she like smoke a pack at a time backstage?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.37,0:21:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No worry of that. She isn't you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.11,0:21:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That was fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.66,0:22:00.49,Default,,0,0,0,,A unique song.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.49,0:22:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to hear a song that normal people can enjoy already.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.48,0:22:06.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You know the next one, Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.61,0:22:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess it from the intro!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.47,0:22:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not another weird song, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.97,0:22:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What was this song again?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.79,0:22:16.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.87,0:22:17.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Kagami.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.56,0:22:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.38,0:22:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's from FMP. FMP.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.99,0:22:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's Kagami's favorite...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:25.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Fumoffu!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.45,0:22:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.51,0:22:28.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I just read the novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.39,0:22:29.91,Default,,0,0,0,,...and got a little hooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.85,0:22:34.97,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,You're really\N good, Kona-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.97,0:22:37.22,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,You can also \Nsound like an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:39.97,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Isn't she just \Ndoing an imitation?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.97,0:22:43.83,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.83,0:22:46.37,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,What are you two going to sing?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.37,0:22:48.19,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,I wonder if there's \Nanything I can sing...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.19,0:22:50.28,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,I don't know many songs...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.28,0:22:51.81,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Anything works.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.81,0:22:52.95,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Look at Konata.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.95,0:22:55.72,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Just sing what you want to!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.72,0:22:56.49,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.49,0:22:58.04,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Then I'll have a look.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.36,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,I'm not very confident \Nabout my singing...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.36,0:23:01.79,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:03.39,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,We're the only \Nones who'll hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.39,0:23:04.81,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Just take it easy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.81,0:23:06.41,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.41,0:23:07.50,Default-Left,,0,0,0,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.80,0:23:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, next time on Lucky Star:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:28.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Tsukasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.75,0:23:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess what?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.63,0:23:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I laughed so hard the other day that I couldn't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.11,0:23:34.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then at school one morning...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.28,0:23:36.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm already out of time?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.17,0:23:37.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time: Motivation Issues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Look forward to next time!
